shutil.copy will copy a specific file from source to destination where as shutil.copytree() will copy the entire directory from source to destination.
2.os.rename() is used to rename the file names
3.shutil will permanently delete the files where as send2trash will move the file to recycle bin in computer.
4.zipFile.open() is the method equivalent to open() in files
5.>>import shutil
    >>import glob
    >>for i in glob.glob(*.pdf):
        shutil.copy(i,destination)